User/kernel questions

Why not directly use memcpy() with user pointers?
Because memcpy() is dangerous, copy_to_user is safer, user-space pointer is not trusted like a kernel space pointer.
_________________________________________
What does copy_from_user() return?
returns 0, if no error. If not successful copy, return number of bytes that could not be copied.
